rubenchristoffer.hetty.html

Class HTMLNodeWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • rubenchristoffer.hetty.html.HTMLNodeWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<HTMLNodeWrapper>, org.w3c.dom.Node
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HTMLDocumentWrapper

    public class HTMLNodeWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.w3c.dom.Node, java.lang.Iterable<HTMLNodeWrapper>
    Wrapper class for HTML DOM Node. Allows for iteration (in a for-each loop or using iterator) Also has a few helper functions.
    Author:
    Ruben Christoffer
